{"tid":2450740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文慎入] 點解就係唔承認自己係負擔！！！！！","createTime":"2021-03-17T15:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T13:02:04.000Z","uid":196574,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"73e7b894cef7f76b79352268cab7f303fcb333b1","tid":2450740,"uid":196574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"近排因為想移民問題同屋企人嘈，一開口已經發哂脾氣話等如無左個仔，話我不孝呢樣個樣，又唔諗下自己係獨生仔，父母都六七十歲，你走左呀連我地骨灰都唔會見倒呀！都唔明，我又無話唔養你地，只係大家居住地唔同，我唔會24小時係你身邊standby啫，家用咪又係照俾。憑咩你地自己無學識，打工要自由要輕鬆唔鐘意湊老闆，搞到無強積金無退休儲備，而家要我用自己一世黎幫你賣單。明明自己生活同依賴重心應該係自己既另一半，因乜解究會完全依賴落仔女度，仲自私到話壓力大咪打份萬幾兩萬既工囉！大佬呀，夠你食定夠我食呀？我係咪成世人唔洗有自己人生，淨係養你地夠呀？你地百老歸老舒舒服服咁走完我自己都可以跟埋gg啦係咪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咁多，其實我都係想問下可以點做啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c45c8f45f5e09586e8b38990938f8631b52fd03","tid":2450740,"uid":126325,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"照移囉 怕乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce57072997b3fd34e4b4804571c1c648f5f6e77c","tid":2450740,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"直接走"},{"pid":"6c99ace13bc4613ae8d4f8dcda5b534322e0660b","tid":2450740,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"想綁你成世係呢個死港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰仔紙仲有冇 玩得狠d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p